2. About the Samples.

This piece is composed of four samples -

   scrape               57.368k
   box_manipulation    212.592k
   proto-synth           6.500k
   proto-bass            9.884k

scrape and box_manipulation were both recorded in the @{"EMRL" Link "EMRL"}
recording studio, using Audition4 and a GVP DSS8 sampler (which gets
surprisingly good results, I might add).  The other two samples were
found on the Aminet (I think) and modified by me to fit this piece.

scrape is a snippet of a CMU rehearsal tape filter and processed beyond
all recognition.

box_manipulation was originally
mic'd with three microphones, and sampled in stereo, then converted to
mono.  It is a recording of a local area DJ thrashing about with a
metal box.

